-- Ace Hires Axa’s Hazard as Client Manager for European Claims
-- B y   M a r c i   J a c o b s
-- 2013-09-23T13:47:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-09-23/ace-hires-axa-s-hazard-as-client-manager-for-european-claims.html
Ace Ltd., the Swiss insurer with
operations in more than 50 nations, appointed Brigitte Hazard to
manage client relationships for continental European claims.  Hazard joins from Axa SA in the newly created role and her
duties for Ace will include being one of the key claims
representatives in France, Ace’s largest market in the region,
the Zurich-based insurer said today in a Business Wire
statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
